ActIndian Act
SubjectSquamish Nation Capilano Indian Reserve No. 5 INTEREST IN LAND AND EASEMENT
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise of the power of the GREATER VANCOUVER SEWERAGE AND DRAINAGE DISTRICT to take an interest in certain lands within Capilano Indian Reserve No. 5; and (b) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the grant of the required easement.
